block.para:
This is the only way to permit multiple permissions at the same time within a stack
      frame because only a single permit at a time can be active on a frame;
      subsequent permits will result in an exception.

example.code:
using System;
using System.Security;
using System.Security.Permissions;

public class PermissionSetToStringExample {
  public static void Main() {

    PermissionSet ps = new PermissionSet(PermissionState.Unrestricted);
    Console.WriteLine(ps.ToString());
  }
}
